{"ja161:0.1":"Jataka ","ja161:0.2":"Dukanipata ","ja161:0.3":"Santhavavagga ","ja161:0.4":"1. Indasamanagottajataka ","ja161:1.1":"“Na santhavam kapurisena kayira, ","ja161:1.2":"Ariyo anariyena pajanamattham; ","ja161:1.3":"Ciranuvutthopi karoti papam, ","ja161:1.4":"Gajo yatha indasamanagottam. ","ja161:2.1":"Yam tveva janna sadiso mamanti, ","ja161:2.2":"Silena pannaya sutena capi; ","ja161:2.3":"Teneva mettim kayiratha saddhim, ","ja161:2.4":"Sukho have sappurisena sangamo”ti. ","ja161:3.1":"Indasamanagottajatakam pathamam. "}